## 1. AUTHENTICATION & ONBOARDING

- [ ] **Cinematic Demo Login works end-to-end** — click "Enter Demo Sandbox," watch it type credentials, confirm it actually calls the real API (check Network tab — should NOT be a fake/simulated delay with no real request) and lands you in a populated dashboard, not an empty one.
- [ ] **Demo account is pre-populated, not empty** — confirm on landing: tasks visible (mix of active/completed/rescheduled), Activity Log has entries already, Velocity DNA chart has real-looking data, credits/level show progression (not Level 1 / 0 credits).
- [ ] **Google Sign-In button is visible and primary** on the login screen — not hidden below other options.
- [ ] **Google Sign-In actually completes OAuth** — click it, go through the real Google consent screen, land back in the app successfully logged in. If this fails or errors, your OAuth redirect URIs in Google Cloud Console don't match your production URL.
- [ ] **Google Sign-In unlocks Calendar access** — after signing in with Google, confirm calendar-dependent features (Command Day, Smart Task Routing) can actually pull real calendar data, not fall back to mock data silently.
- [ ] **Email/password login still works** (if it exists as a separate option) as a fallback path.
- [ ] **Logout works and actually clears session** — log out, confirm you're returned to login screen and can't navigate back into the dashboard via browser back button.

