## 3. LIVE TRACKING & ALERTS

- [ ] **Live Pace Tracking sparklines render** on task cards and visibly differ between tasks (not all identical/flat).
- [ ] **LIVE badge appears** on a task you've made critically behind-pace (test by either waiting for a seeded critical task or manually adjusting one to trigger it).
- [ ] **Velocity Degradation Alerts fire** — confirm a toast notification appears when a task's status crosses from green→amber or amber→red. You may need to wait for the 60-second recalculation cycle or manipulate a task's deadline/progress to force a state change.
- [ ] **Burnout Horizon Chart renders correctly** — 14-day view shows a required-vs-available-hours comparison, and if you're seeded to be over capacity, it visibly pulses red and offers a triage action.
- [ ] **Trust Score Check-ins comparison works** — self-reported progress vs actual subtask completion produces a visible recalibration when they diverge significantly.

