## 5. AGENTIC AUTONOMY — ACTIVITY LOG & CORE AUTONOMOUS ACTIONS

- [ ] **Activity Log page is easy to find** — accessible from main nav or header, not buried.
- [ ] **Activity Log is pre-populated on demo login** with multiple realistic entries (not empty, not just 1-2 sparse entries).
- [ ] **Every log entry shows timestamp + plain-English reason** — no entry should be cryptic or missing context.
- [ ] **Undo button works on at least one loggable action** — trigger an undoable autonomous action, click Undo, confirm the action is actually reversed (task/schedule/email state reverts), not just the toast disappearing.
- [ ] **Command Day auto-rebalance triggers automatically** — open Command Day with a seeded RED task present. Confirm it reorganizes the schedule WITHOUT you clicking anything, and shows the "AUTONOMOUS — acted without being asked" banner.
- [ ] **AI Rebalance reasoning sentence displays** — confirm the one-sentence Gemini explanation for why blocks were reordered actually appears and makes sense (not generic boilerplate).

