## 6. COMPOSITIONAL ACTION CHAINS

- [ ] **Cascading chain triggers correctly** — create or seed a scenario where Rebalance cannot fully resolve a conflict (two tasks still collide after reordering). Confirm it automatically cascades into drafting a Negotiate email.
- [ ] **Chain logs as ONE expandable entry**, not three separate flat entries — confirm the Activity Log shows a single card that expands to reveal the 3-step causal trace (Rebalanced → Still conflicted → Drafted extension).
- [ ] **Each step in the chain has correct timestamps** that make causal sense (step 2 after step 1, step 3 after step 2, not simultaneous or out of order).
- [ ] **Undo on a chained action works correctly** — confirm undoing a step behaves sensibly (does it undo just that step, or the whole chain? Test and confirm the behavior matches what the UI implies it will do).

