## 9. REASONING TRACE

- [ ] **"Why this, not something else?" section appears on log entries** — expand a log entry, confirm there's a visible alternatives-considered section.
- [ ] **At least 1-2 rejected alternatives shown per entry**, each with a one-line reason — not empty, not just repeating the chosen action.
- [ ] **Reasoning traces appear on seeded entries too** — confirm this isn't only generated live, but pre-populated in the demo account's existing log history (you specified 12+ entries should have this).

